<br>
                  Quite a few high end zones ( of GoD) got beta tested by a few guilds I won't name. They were copied on test server a bit ago ( one month or so). Needless to say the spoiler level after this is seriously high. There isn't much challengein completing an event once you have tested it with a dev asking if this or that was ok and naturally having to explain the in and out of the event.<br>
<br>
                   So either way its hard to fix because once again, if SOE has the expansion beta tested by some guilds they reduce the life of their expansion by a lot ( spoilers for the beta test guilds which spread to all the top guilds of the servers and the whole game fairly fast). <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=228771">65 Maestro Kinuvan the Minstrel</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
